{"tid":2345967,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"又係奧巴馬》參議院揭發奧巴馬借宣明會　資助阿爾蓋達恐怖份子","createTime":"2020-12-30T03:03:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T04:39:52.000Z","uid":35519,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6983a72b62a92e8f524470360cbc56a020d7e8f5","tid":2345967,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T03:03:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">參議院揭發奧巴馬借宣明會 <br />\n資助阿爾蓋達分身組織</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/dwMg6Dyg1Ez0B1hohfVexg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTQxMS40NzE2OTgxMTMyMDc1NA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/ixgTiZ8D7.pm8PCiH2Bqzg--~B/aD00NjQ7dz03OTU7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/en-US/the_national_review_738/afb074bbc4ed723bd560369b83362b4a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FdwMg6Dyg1Ez0B1hohfVexg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTQxMS40NzE2OTgxMTMyMDc1NA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FixgTiZ8D7.pm8PCiH2Bqzg--~B%2FaD00NjQ7dz03OTU7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen-US%2Fthe_national_review_738%2Fafb074bbc4ed723bd560369b83362b4a&h=65f8bab1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.yahoo.com/senate-investigation-finds-obama-admin-201648458.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.yahoo.com%2Fsenate-investigation-finds-obama-admin-201648458.html&d=WZfMoUUHHVTN90V%2FD%2BJOGS8TOYGSXSADKPC8%2B0d5FCk%3D&h=bbe0ed66\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.yahoo.com/senate-investigation-finds-obama-admin-201648458.html</a><br />\n<br />\n根據參議院的最新報告，人道機構美國世界宣明會（World Vision）在獲得奧巴馬政府批准後於2014年與Islamic Relief Agency (ISRA)進行了不當交易，明知該組織與與恐怖主義關連並受制裁的情況下，仍為其提供美國政府資助。<br />\n<br />\n參議院財政委員會主席Charles E. Grassley最近發表報告，詳細說明他及同僚自2019年2月開始對世界宣明會與ISRA之間的關係進行調查的結果。<br />\n<br />\n調查發現，世界宣明會沒有了解ISRA因為接受拉登控制的Maktab al-Khidamat組織(阿爾蓋達的前身)匯入500萬美元，所以自2004年以來已受到美國制裁，然而，報告指出這種失誤是由於缺失適當審查程序所導致。<br />\n<br />\n是次調查是由2018年7月《National Review》專欄引發，其伊斯蘭觀察組織主任Sam Westrop詳細說明他們的調查結果&mdash;&mdash;即奧巴馬政府將20萬美元的納稅人公帑授予ISRA。<br />\n<br />\nSam Westrop寫道「政府官員即使明知這是一個恐怖組織，仍特別授權釋放『至少115,000美元』的贈款」。<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n參議員Charles E. Grassley的報告原文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.finance.senate.gov/imo/media/doc/Oversight,%2012-23-20,%20Memo%20on%20World%20Vision%20Investigation.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.finance.senate.gov%2Fimo%2Fmedia%2Fdoc%2FOversight%2C%252012-23-20%2C%2520Memo%2520on%2520World%2520Vision%2520Investigation.pdf&d=WZfMoUUHHVTN90V%2FD%2BJOGS8TOYGSXSADKPC8%2B0d5FCk%3D&h=8dbba2f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.finance.senate.gov/imo/media/doc/Oversight,%2012-23-20,%20Memo%20on%20World%20Vision%20Investigation.pdf</a>　"},{"pid":"78b59b70f543273887192f525682728f11125a43","tid":2345967,"uid":134119,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T03:04:31.000Z","msg":"死力架，快撚d 死啦閪窿馬"},{"pid":"4ca163746700fafaa78753114c2e561063995607","tid":2345967,"uid":83713,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T03:06:04.000Z","msg":"唉，我一早知宣明會有問題架啦！不過呢..."},{"pid":"f03a2b39a327ddbf979439a5d08f8a508363e45a","tid":2345967,"uid":35519,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T03:06:06.000Z","msg":"新聞相關熱門Tweet<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/paulsperry_/status/1344060755298156545\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpaulsperry_%2Fstatus%2F1344060755298156545&d=WZfMoUUHHVTN90V%2FD%2BJOGS8TOYGSXSADKPC8%2B0d5FCk%3D&h=c5f2e5ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpaulsperry_%2Fstatus%2F1344060755298156545&h=4a6a19e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/paulsperry_/status/1344060755298156545</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=Obama%20%20al-Qaeda&amp;src=typed_query\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3DObama%2520%2520al-Qaeda%